reviews: Really is a nice hat, decent quality and no problems - well, almost. I'm only giving 3 stars because if I had known how tall (and structured) it is, I wouldn't have bought it. I'll keep it and use it as a back-up for the perfect hat that I'm still searching for - my last perfect one saved me from a bird bombardment, and even after a thorough cleaning, it just isn't the same (and I don't just mean the discolouration).
product_name: JAMONT Unisex Cotton Adjustable Plain Hat Baseball Cap Multi Colors

review_title: Quality hat. Only issue is it catches lint easily.
reviews: Bought two hats from different sellers on Amazon. The other one was harder and thicker material which caused irritation were my ears rubbed on the edge. This one is much more comfortable. Seems durable, too. Only complaint is the finish of the material seems to catch a lot of lint and pet hair that is hard to remove.
product_name: JAMONT Unisex Cotton Adjustable Plain Hat Baseball Cap Multi Colors

review_title: this one i like the best
reviews: i bought three hats to try out .... this one i like the best ..... the others have a upside down bowl appearance to them which really don't like (right up there with wearing them backwards :) Probably going to order at least one more in a different color. Shipping was great as usual (except when amazon uses intelcom)
product_name: JAMONT Unisex Cotton Adjustable Plain Hat Baseball Cap Multi Colors

reviews: Product arrived exactly how it looked in the pictures. This is probably one of my new favorite go-to caps for its quality and fit. It's got a stiff crown and is high-profile, so if you have a small head I can see these hats being a tad too big for you. I have a big head so this hat is perfect for me.
product_name: JAMONT Unisex Cotton Adjustable Plain Hat Baseball Cap Multi Colors

review_title: Hat fits pretty good, but will be sending it back
reviews:
Hat fits pretty good, but will be sending it back.
My "Light Grey" showed up as a "Faint Purple".
This wasn't my mistake by wrong colour choice....it just was an attempt at a greyish colour.
product_name: JAMONT Unisex Cotton Adjustable Plain Hat Baseball Cap Multi Colors

reviews:
Bought it for my son but I liked it so I kept it for myself !
Thank you, Amazon !

reviews: Be aware if you like your ball cap to sit down on your head this one isn't for you. The lining in the front of the cap makes it stiff and it sits up too high and has 3 points. Not liking it. Material is good, color is good.
product_name: JAMONT Unisex Cotton Adjustable Plain Hat Baseball Cap Multi Colors

review_title: Slightly smaller than expected, not enought to prevent wearing.
reviews: Decent, not defects. I found that despite the capacity to be adjusted the circumference is a tad to small, so it feel a bit tight around my head.
product_name: JAMONT Unisex Cotton Adjustable Plain Hat Baseball Cap Multi Colors

reviews: Made for people with gigantic heads
product_name: JAMONT Unisex Cotton Adjustable Plain Hat Baseball Cap Multi Colors

reviews: Really is a nice hat, decent quality and no problems - well, almost. I'm only giving 3 stars because if I had known how tall (and structured) it is, I wouldn't have bought it. I'll keep it and use it as a back-up for the perfect hat that I'm still searching for - my last perfect one saved me from a bird bombardment, and even after a thorough cleaning, it just isn't the same (and I don't just mean the discolouration).
product_name: JAMONT Unisex Cotton Adjustable Plain Hat Baseball Cap Multi Colors

review_title: Quality hat. Only issue is it catches lint easily.
reviews: Bought two hats from different sellers on Amazon. The other one was harder and thicker material which caused irritation were my ears rubbed on the edge. This one is much more comfortable. Seems durable, too. Only complaint is the finish of the material seems to catch a lot of lint and pet hair that is hard to remove.
product_name: JAMONT Unisex Cotton Adjustable Plain Hat Baseball Cap Multi Colors

review_title: this one i like the best
reviews: i bought three hats to try out .... this one i like the best ..... the others have a upside down bowl appearance to them which really don't like (right up there with wearing them backwards :) Probably going to order at least one more in a different color. Shipping was great as usual (except when amazon uses intelcom)
product_name: JAMONT Unisex Cotton Adjustable Plain Hat Baseball Cap Multi Colors

reviews: Product arrived exactly how it looked in the pictures. This is probably one of my new favorite go-to caps for its quality and fit. It's got a stiff crown and is high-profile, so if you have a small head I can see these hats being a tad too big for you. I have a big head so this hat is perfect for me.
product_name: JAMONT Unisex Cotton Adjustable Plain Hat Baseball Cap Multi Colors

review_title: Hat fits pretty good, but will be sending it back
reviews:
Hat fits pretty good, but will be sending it back.
My "Light Grey" showed up as a "Faint Purple".
This wasn't my mistake by wrong colour choice....it just was an attempt at a greyish colour.
product_name: JAMONT Unisex Cotton Adjustable Plain Hat Baseball Cap Multi Colors

reviews:
Bought it for my son but I liked it so I kept it for myself !
Thank you, Amazon !

Seems durable, too. Only complaint is the finish of the material seems to catch a lot of lint and pet hair that is hard to remove.
product_name: JAMONT Unisex Cotton Adjustable Plain Hat Baseball Cap Multi Colors

review_title: this one i like the best
reviews: i bought three hats to try out .... this one i like the best ..... the others have a upside down bowl appearance to them which really don't like (right up there with wearing them backwards :) Probably going to order at least one more in a different color. Shipping was great as usual (except when amazon uses intelcom)
product_name: JAMONT Unisex Cotton Adjustable Plain Hat Baseball Cap Multi Colors

reviews: Product arrived exactly how it looked in the pictures. This is probably one of my new favorite go-to caps for its quality and fit. It's got a stiff crown and is high-profile, so if you have a small head I can see these hats being a tad too big for you. I have a big head so this hat is perfect for me.
product_name: JAMONT Unisex Cotton Adjustable Plain Hat Baseball Cap Multi Colors

review_title: Hat fits pretty good, but will be sending it back
reviews:
Hat fits pretty good, but will be sending it back.
My "Light Grey" showed up as a "Faint Purple".
This wasn't my mistake by wrong colour choice....it just was an attempt at a greyish colour.
product_name: JAMONT Unisex Cotton Adjustable Plain Hat Baseball Cap Multi Colors

reviews:
Bought it for my son but I liked it so I kept it for myself !
Thank you, Amazon !
Lisa Benedix, Grand Lake NB

It's got a stiff crown and is high-profile, so if you have a small head I can see these hats being a tad too big for you. I have a big head so this hat is perfect for me.
product_name: JAMONT Unisex Cotton Adjustable Plain Hat Baseball Cap Multi Colors

review_title: Hat fits pretty good, but will be sending it back
reviews:
Hat fits pretty good, but will be sending it back.
My "Light Grey" showed up as a "Faint Purple".
This wasn't my mistake by wrong colour choice....it just was an attempt at a greyish colour.
product_name: JAMONT Unisex Cotton Adjustable Plain Hat Baseball Cap Multi Colors

reviews:
Bought it for my son but I liked it so I kept it for myself !
Thank you, Amazon !
Lisa Benedix, Grand Lake NB
product_name: JAMONT Unisex Cotton Adjustable Plain Hat Baseball Cap Multi Colors

reviews: specified size does not match
product_name: JAMONT Unisex Cotton Adjustable Plain Hat Baseball Cap Multi Colors

reviews: Be aware if you like your ball cap to sit down on your head this one isn't for you. The lining in the front of the cap makes it stiff and it sits up too high and has 3 points. Not liking it. Material is good, color is good.
product_name: JAMONT Unisex Cotton Adjustable Plain Hat Baseball Cap Multi Colors

review_title: Slightly smaller than expected, not enought to prevent wearing.
reviews: Decent, not defects. I found that despite the capacity to be adjusted the circumference is a tad to small, so it feel a bit tight around my head.
product_name: JAMONT Unisex Cotton Adjustable Plain Hat Baseball Cap Multi Colors

reviews: Made for people with gigantic heads
product_name: JAMONT Unisex Cotton Adjustable Plain Hat Baseball Cap Multi Colors

reviews: Really is a nice hat, decent quality and no problems - well, almost. I'm only giving 3 stars because if I had known how tall (and structured) it is, I wouldn't have bought it. I'll keep it and use it as a back-up for the perfect hat that I'm still searching for - my last perfect one saved me from a bird bombardment, and even after a thorough cleaning, it just isn't the same (and I don't just mean the discolouration).
product_name: JAMONT Unisex Cotton Adjustable Plain Hat Baseball Cap Multi Colors

review_title: Quality hat. Only issue is it catches lint easily.
reviews: Bought two hats from different sellers on Amazon. The other one was harder and thicker material which caused irritation were my ears rubbed on the edge. This one is much more comfortable. Seems durable, too. Only complaint is the finish of the material seems to catch a lot of lint and pet hair that is hard to remove.
product_name: JAMONT Unisex Cotton Adjustable Plain Hat Baseball Cap Multi Colors

review_title: this one i like the best
reviews: i bought three hats to try out .... this one i like the best ..... the others have a upside down bowl appearance to them which really don't like (right up there with wearing them backwards :) Probably going to order at least one more in a different color. Shipping was great as usual (except when amazon uses intelcom)

reviews: Bought two hats from different sellers on Amazon. The other one was harder and thicker material which caused irritation were my ears rubbed on the edge. This one is much more comfortable. Seems durable, too. Only complaint is the finish of the material seems to catch a lot of lint and pet hair that is hard to remove.
product_name: JAMONT Unisex Cotton Adjustable Plain Hat Baseball Cap Multi Colors

review_title: this one i like the best
reviews: i bought three hats to try out .... this one i like the best ..... the others have a upside down bowl appearance to them which really don't like (right up there with wearing them backwards :) Probably going to order at least one more in a different color. Shipping was great as usual (except when amazon uses intelcom)
product_name: JAMONT Unisex Cotton Adjustable Plain Hat Baseball Cap Multi Colors

reviews: Product arrived exactly how it looked in the pictures. This is probably one of my new favorite go-to caps for its quality and fit. It's got a stiff crown and is high-profile, so if you have a small head I can see these hats being a tad too big for you. I have a big head so this hat is perfect for me.
product_name: JAMONT Unisex Cotton Adjustable Plain Hat Baseball Cap Multi Colors

review_title: Hat fits pretty good, but will be sending it back
reviews:
Hat fits pretty good, but will be sending it back.
My "Light Grey" showed up as a "Faint Purple".
This wasn't my mistake by wrong colour choice....it just was an attempt at a greyish colour.
product_name: JAMONT Unisex Cotton Adjustable Plain Hat Baseball Cap Multi Colors

reviews:
Bought it for my son but I liked it so I kept it for myself !
Thank you, Amazon !
Lisa Benedix, Grand Lake NB
product_name: JAMONT Unisex Cotton Adjustable Plain Hat Baseball Cap Multi Colors

reviews: specified size does not match
product_name: JAMONT Unisex Cotton Adjustable Plain Hat Baseball Cap Multi Colors

reviews: Be aware if you like your ball cap to sit down on your head this one isn't for you. The lining in the front of the cap makes it stiff and it sits up too high and has 3 points. Not liking it. Material is good, color is good.
product_name: JAMONT Unisex Cotton Adjustable Plain Hat Baseball Cap Multi Colors

review_title: Slightly smaller than expected, not enought to prevent wearing.
reviews: Decent, not defects. I found that despite the capacity to be adjusted the circumference is a tad to small, so it feel a bit tight around my head.
product_name: JAMONT Unisex Cotton Adjustable Plain Hat Baseball Cap Multi Colors

reviews: Made for people with gigantic heads
product_name: JAMONT Unisex Cotton Adjustable Plain Hat Baseball Cap Multi Colors

reviews: Really is a nice hat, decent quality and no problems - well, almost. I'm only giving 3 stars because if I had known how tall (and structured) it is, I wouldn't have bought it. I'll keep it and use it as a back-up for the perfect hat that I'm still searching for - my last perfect one saved me from a bird bombardment, and even after a thorough cleaning, it just isn't the same (and I don't just mean the discolouration).

product_name: JAMONT Unisex Cotton Adjustable Plain Hat Baseball Cap Multi Colors

reviews: Made for people with gigantic heads
product_name: JAMONT Unisex Cotton Adjustable Plain Hat Baseball Cap Multi Colors

reviews: Really is a nice hat, decent quality and no problems - well, almost. I'm only giving 3 stars because if I had known how tall (and structured) it is, I wouldn't have bought it. I'll keep it and use it as a back-up for the perfect hat that I'm still searching for - my last perfect one saved me from a bird bombardment, and even after a thorough cleaning, it just isn't the same (and I don't just mean the discolouration).
product_name: JAMONT Unisex Cotton Adjustable Plain Hat Baseball Cap Multi Colors

review_title: Quality hat. Only issue is it catches lint easily.
reviews: Bought two hats from different sellers on Amazon. The other one was harder and thicker material which caused irritation were my ears rubbed on the edge. This one is much more comfortable. Seems durable, too. Only complaint is the finish of the material seems to catch a lot of lint and pet hair that is hard to remove.
product_name: JAMONT Unisex Cotton Adjustable Plain Hat Baseball Cap Multi Colors

review_title: this one i like the best
reviews: i bought three hats to try out .... this one i like the best ..... the others have a upside down bowl appearance to them which really don't like (right up there with wearing them backwards :) Probably going to order at least one more in a different color. Shipping was great as usual (except when amazon uses intelcom)
product_name: JAMONT Unisex Cotton Adjustable Plain Hat Baseball Cap Multi Colors

reviews: Product arrived exactly how it looked in the pictures. This is probably one of my new favorite go-to caps for its quality and fit. It's got a stiff crown and is high-profile, so if you have a small head I can see these hats being a tad too big for you. I have a big head so this hat is perfect for me.
product_name: JAMONT Unisex Cotton Adjustable Plain Hat Baseball Cap Multi Colors

reviews: Be aware if you like your ball cap to sit down on your head this one isn't for you. The lining in the front of the cap makes it stiff and it sits up too high and has 3 points. Not liking it. Material is good, color is good.
product_name: JAMONT Unisex Cotton Adjustable Plain Hat Baseball Cap Multi Colors

review_title: Slightly smaller than expected, not enought to prevent wearing.
reviews: Decent, not defects. I found that despite the capacity to be adjusted the circumference is a tad to small, so it feel a bit tight around my head.
product_name: JAMONT Unisex Cotton Adjustable Plain Hat Baseball Cap Multi Colors

reviews: Made for people with gigantic heads
product_name: JAMONT Unisex Cotton Adjustable Plain Hat Baseball Cap Multi Colors

reviews: Really is a nice hat, decent quality and no problems - well, almost. I'm only giving 3 stars because if I had known how tall (and structured) it is, I wouldn't have bought it. I'll keep it and use it as a back-up for the perfect hat that I'm still searching for - my last perfect one saved me from a bird bombardment, and even after a thorough cleaning, it just isn't the same (and I don't just mean the discolouration).
product_name: JAMONT Unisex Cotton Adjustable Plain Hat Baseball Cap Multi Colors

review_title: Quality hat. Only issue is it catches lint easily.
reviews: Bought two hats from different sellers on Amazon. The other one was harder and thicker material which caused irritation were my ears rubbed on the edge. This one is much more comfortable. Seems durable, too. Only complaint is the finish of the material seems to catch a lot of lint and pet hair that is hard to remove.
product_name: JAMONT Unisex Cotton Adjustable Plain Hat Baseball Cap Multi Colors

review_title: this one i like the best
reviews: i bought three hats to try out .... this one i like the best ..... the others have a upside down bowl appearance to them which really don't like (right up there with wearing them backwards :) Probably going to order at least one more in a different color. Shipping was great as usual (except when amazon uses intelcom)
product_name: JAMONT Unisex Cotton Adjustable Plain Hat Baseball Cap Multi Colors

reviews: Product arrived exactly how it looked in the pictures. This is probably one of my new favorite go-to caps for its quality and fit. It's got a stiff crown and is high-profile, so if you have a small head I can see these hats being a tad too big for you. I have a big head so this hat is perfect for me.

reviews: Bought two hats from different sellers on Amazon. The other one was harder and thicker material which caused irritation were my ears rubbed on the edge. This one is much more comfortable. Seems durable, too. Only complaint is the finish of the material seems to catch a lot of lint and pet hair that is hard to remove.
product_name: JAMONT Unisex Cotton Adjustable Plain Hat Baseball Cap Multi Colors

review_title: this one i like the best
reviews: i bought three hats to try out .... this one i like the best ..... the others have a upside down bowl appearance to them which really don't like (right up there with wearing them backwards :) Probably going to order at least one more in a different color. Shipping was great as usual (except when amazon uses intelcom)
product_name: JAMONT Unisex Cotton Adjustable Plain Hat Baseball Cap Multi Colors

reviews: Product arrived exactly how it looked in the pictures. This is probably one of my new favorite go-to caps for its quality and fit. It's got a stiff crown and is high-profile, so if you have a small head I can see these hats being a tad too big for you. I have a big head so this hat is perfect for me.
product_name: JAMONT Unisex Cotton Adjustable Plain Hat Baseball Cap Multi Colors

review_title: Hat fits pretty good, but will be sending it back
reviews:
Hat fits pretty good, but will be sending it back.
My "Light Grey" showed up as a "Faint Purple".
This wasn't my mistake by wrong colour choice....it just was an attempt at a greyish colour.
product_name: JAMONT Unisex Cotton Adjustable Plain Hat Baseball Cap Multi Colors

reviews:
Bought it for my son but I liked it so I kept it for myself !
Thank you, Amazon !
Lisa Benedix, Grand Lake NB
product_name: JAMONT Unisex Cotton Adjustable Plain Hat Baseball Cap Multi Colors

reviews: specified size does not match
product_name: JAMONT Unisex Cotton Adjustable Plain Hat Baseball Cap Multi Colors

reviews: Be aware if you like your ball cap to sit down on your head this one isn't for you. The lining in the front of the cap makes it stiff and it sits up too high and has 3 points. Not liking it. Material is good, color is good.
product_name: JAMONT Unisex Cotton Adjustable Plain Hat Baseball Cap Multi Colors

review_title: Slightly smaller than expected, not enought to prevent wearing.
reviews: Decent, not defects. I found that despite the capacity to be adjusted the circumference is a tad to small, so it feel a bit tight around my head.
product_name: JAMONT Unisex Cotton Adjustable Plain Hat Baseball Cap Multi Colors

reviews: Made for people with gigantic heads
product_name: JAMONT Unisex Cotton Adjustable Plain Hat Baseball Cap Multi Colors

reviews: Really is a nice hat, decent quality and no problems - well, almost. I'm only giving 3 stars because if I had known how tall (and structured) it is, I wouldn't have bought it. I'll keep it and use it as a back-up for the perfect hat that I'm still searching for - my last perfect one saved me from a bird bombardment, and even after a thorough cleaning, it just isn't the same (and I don't just mean the discolouration).

product_name: JAMONT Unisex Cotton Adjustable Plain Hat Baseball Cap Multi Colors

reviews: Made for people with gigantic heads
product_name: JAMONT Unisex Cotton Adjustable Plain Hat Baseball Cap Multi Colors

reviews: Really is a nice hat, decent quality and no problems - well, almost. I'm only giving 3 stars because if I had known how tall (and structured) it is, I wouldn't have bought it. I'll keep it and use it as a back-up for the perfect hat that I'm still searching for - my last perfect one saved me from a bird bombardment, and even after a thorough cleaning, it just isn't the same (and I don't just mean the discolouration).
product_name: JAMONT Unisex Cotton Adjustable Plain Hat Baseball Cap Multi Colors

review_title: Quality hat. Only issue is it catches lint easily.
reviews: Bought two hats from different sellers on Amazon. The other one was harder and thicker material which caused irritation were my ears rubbed on the edge. This one is much more comfortable. Seems durable, too. Only complaint is the finish of the material seems to catch a lot of lint and pet hair that is hard to remove.
product_name: JAMONT Unisex Cotton Adjustable Plain Hat Baseball Cap Multi Colors

review_title: this one i like the best
reviews: i bought three hats to try out .... this one i like the best ..... the others have a upside down bowl appearance to them which really don't like (right up there with wearing them backwards :) Probably going to order at least one more in a different color. Shipping was great as usual (except when amazon uses intelcom)
product_name: JAMONT Unisex Cotton Adjustable Plain Hat Baseball Cap Multi Colors

reviews: Product arrived exactly how it looked in the pictures. This is probably one of my new favorite go-to caps for its quality and fit. It's got a stiff crown and is high-profile, so if you have a small head I can see these hats being a tad too big for you. I have a big head so this hat is perfect for me.
product_name: JAMONT Unisex Cotton Adjustable Plain Hat Baseball Cap Multi Colors

reviews: Be aware if you like your ball cap to sit down on your head this one isn't for you. The lining in the front of the cap makes it stiff and it sits up too high and has 3 points. Not liking it. Material is good, color is good.
product_name: JAMONT Unisex Cotton Adjustable Plain Hat Baseball Cap Multi Colors

review_title: Slightly smaller than expected, not enought to prevent wearing.
reviews: Decent, not defects. I found that despite the capacity to be adjusted the circumference is a tad to small, so it feel a bit tight around my head.
product_name: JAMONT Unisex Cotton Adjustable Plain Hat Baseball Cap Multi Colors

reviews: Made for people with gigantic heads
product_name: JAMONT Unisex Cotton Adjustable Plain Hat Baseball Cap Multi Colors

reviews: Really is a nice hat, decent quality and no problems - well, almost. I'm only giving 3 stars because if I had known how tall (and structured) it is, I wouldn't have bought it. I'll keep it and use it as a back-up for the perfect hat that I'm still searching for - my last perfect one saved me from a bird bombardment, and even after a thorough cleaning, it just isn't the same (and I don't just mean the discolouration).
product_name: JAMONT Unisex Cotton Adjustable Plain Hat Baseball Cap Multi Colors

review_title: Quality hat. Only issue is it catches lint easily.
reviews: Bought two hats from different sellers on Amazon. The other one was harder and thicker material which caused irritation were my ears rubbed on the edge. This one is much more comfortable. Seems durable, too. Only complaint is the finish of the material seems to catch a lot of lint and pet hair that is hard to remove.
product_name: JAMONT Unisex Cotton Adjustable Plain Hat Baseball Cap Multi Colors

review_title: this one i like the best
reviews: i bought three hats to try out .... this one i like the best ..... the others have a upside down bowl appearance to them which really don't like (right up there with wearing them backwards :) Probably going to order at least one more in a different color. Shipping was great as usual (except when amazon uses intelcom)
product_name: JAMONT Unisex Cotton Adjustable Plain Hat Baseball Cap Multi Colors

reviews: Product arrived exactly how it looked in the pictures. This is probably one of my new favorite go-to caps for its quality and fit. It's got a stiff crown and is high-profile, so if you have a small head I can see these hats being a tad too big for you. I have a big head so this hat is perfect for me.

reviews: Bought two hats from different sellers on Amazon. The other one was harder and thicker material which caused irritation were my ears rubbed on the edge. This one is much more comfortable. Seems durable, too. Only complaint is the finish of the material seems to catch a lot of lint and pet hair that is hard to remove.
product_name: JAMONT Unisex Cotton Adjustable Plain Hat Baseball Cap Multi Colors

review_title: this one i like the best
reviews: i bought three hats to try out .... this one i like the best ..... the others have a upside down bowl appearance to them which really don't like (right up there with wearing them backwards :) Probably going to order at least one more in a different color. Shipping was great as usual (except when amazon uses intelcom)
product_name: JAMONT Unisex Cotton Adjustable Plain Hat Baseball Cap Multi Colors

reviews: Product arrived exactly how it looked in the pictures. This is probably one of my new favorite go-to caps for its quality and fit. It's got a stiff crown and is high-profile, so if you have a small head I can see these hats being a tad too big for you. I have a big head so this hat is perfect for me.
product_name: JAMONT Unisex Cotton Adjustable Plain Hat Baseball Cap Multi Colors

review_title: Hat fits pretty good, but will be sending it back
reviews:
Hat fits pretty good, but will be sending it back.
My "Light Grey" showed up as a "Faint Purple".
This wasn't my mistake by wrong colour choice....it just was an attempt at a greyish colour.
product_name: JAMONT Unisex Cotton Adjustable Plain Hat Baseball Cap Multi Colors

reviews:
Bought it for my son but I liked it so I kept it for myself !
Thank you, Amazon !
Lisa Benedix, Grand Lake NB
product_name: JAMONT Unisex Cotton Adjustable Plain Hat Baseball Cap Multi Colors

reviews: specified size does not match
product_name: JAMONT Unisex Cotton Adjustable Plain Hat Baseball Cap Multi Colors

reviews: Be aware if you like your ball cap to sit down on your head this one isn't for you. The lining in the front of the cap makes it stiff and it sits up too high and has 3 points. Not liking it. Material is good, color is good.
product_name: JAMONT Unisex Cotton Adjustable Plain Hat Baseball Cap Multi Colors

review_title: Slightly smaller than expected, not enought to prevent wearing.
reviews: Decent, not defects. I found that despite the capacity to be adjusted the circumference is a tad to small, so it feel a bit tight around my head.
product_name: JAMONT Unisex Cotton Adjustable Plain Hat Baseball Cap Multi Colors

reviews: Made for people with gigantic heads
product_name: JAMONT Unisex Cotton Adjustable Plain Hat Baseball Cap Multi Colors

reviews: Really is a nice hat, decent quality and no problems - well, almost. I'm only giving 3 stars because if I had known how tall (and structured) it is, I wouldn't have bought it. I'll keep it and use it as a back-up for the perfect hat that I'm still searching for - my last perfect one saved me from a bird bombardment, and even after a thorough cleaning, it just isn't the same (and I don't just mean the discolouration).

product_name: JAMONT Unisex Cotton Adjustable Plain Hat Baseball Cap Multi Colors

reviews: Made for people with gigantic heads
product_name: JAMONT Unisex Cotton Adjustable Plain Hat Baseball Cap Multi Colors

reviews: Really is a nice hat, decent quality and no problems - well, almost. I'm only giving 3 stars because if I had known how tall (and structured) it is, I wouldn't have bought it. I'll keep it and use it as a back-up for the perfect hat that I'm still searching for - my last perfect one saved me from a bird bombardment, and even after a thorough cleaning, it just isn't the same (and I don't just mean the discolouration).
product_name: JAMONT Unisex Cotton Adjustable Plain Hat Baseball Cap Multi Colors

review_title: Quality hat. Only issue is it catches lint easily.
reviews: Bought two hats from different sellers on Amazon. The other one was harder and thicker material which caused irritation were my ears rubbed on the edge. This one is much more comfortable. Seems durable, too. Only complaint is the finish of the material seems to catch a lot of lint and pet hair that is hard to remove.
product_name: JAMONT Unisex Cotton Adjustable Plain Hat Baseball Cap Multi Colors

review_title: this one i like the best
reviews: i bought three hats to try out .... this one i like the best ..... the others have a upside down bowl appearance to them which really don't like (right up there with wearing them backwards :) Probably going to order at least one more in a different color. Shipping was great as usual (except when amazon uses intelcom)
product_name: JAMONT Unisex Cotton Adjustable Plain Hat Baseball Cap Multi Colors

reviews: Product arrived exactly how it looked in the pictures. This is probably one of my new favorite go-to caps for its quality and fit. It's got a stiff crown and is high-profile, so if you have a small head I can see these hats being a tad too big for you. I have a big head so this hat is perfect for me.
product_name: JAMONT Unisex Cotton Adjustable Plain Hat Baseball Cap Multi Colors

reviews: Be aware if you like your ball cap to sit down on your head this one isn't for you. The lining in the front of the cap makes it stiff and it sits up too high and has 3 points. Not liking it. Material is good, color is good.
product_name: JAMONT Unisex Cotton Adjustable Plain Hat Baseball Cap Multi Colors

review_title: Slightly smaller than expected, not enought to prevent wearing.
reviews: Decent, not defects. I found that despite the capacity to be adjusted the circumference is a tad to small, so it feel a bit tight around my head.
product_name: JAMONT Unisex Cotton Adjustable Plain Hat Baseball Cap Multi Colors

reviews: Made for people with gigantic heads
product_name: JAMONT Unisex Cotton Adjustable Plain Hat Baseball Cap Multi Colors

reviews: Really is a nice hat, decent quality and no problems - well, almost. I'm only giving 3 stars because if I had known how tall (and structured) it is, I wouldn't have bought it. I'll keep it and use it as a back-up for the perfect hat that I'm still searching for - my last perfect one saved me from a bird bombardment, and even after a thorough cleaning, it just isn't the same (and I don't just mean the discolouration).
product_name: JAMONT Unisex Cotton Adjustable Plain Hat Baseball Cap Multi Colors

review_title: Quality hat. Only issue is it catches lint easily.
reviews: Bought two hats from different sellers on Amazon. The other one was harder and thicker material which caused irritation were my ears rubbed on the edge. This one is much more comfortable. Seems durable, too. Only complaint is the finish of the material seems to catch a lot of lint and pet hair that is hard to remove.
product_name: JAMONT Unisex Cotton Adjustable Plain Hat Baseball Cap Multi Colors

review_title: this one i like the best
reviews: i bought three hats to try out .... this one i like the best ..... the others have a upside down bowl appearance to them which really don't like (right up there with wearing them backwards :) Probably going to order at least one more in a different color. Shipping was great as usual (except when amazon uses intelcom)
product_name: JAMONT Unisex Cotton Adjustable Plain Hat Baseball Cap Multi Colors

reviews: Product arrived exactly how it looked in the pictures. This is probably one of my new favorite go-to caps for its quality and fit. It's got a stiff crown and is high-profile, so if you have a small head I can see these hats being a tad too big for you. I have a big head so this hat is perfect for me.

reviews: Bought two hats from different sellers on Amazon. The other one was harder and thicker material which caused irritation were my ears rubbed on the edge. This one is much more comfortable. Seems durable, too. Only complaint is the finish of the material seems to catch a lot of lint and pet hair that is hard to remove.
product_name: JAMONT Unisex Cotton Adjustable Plain Hat Baseball Cap Multi Colors

review_title: this one i like the best
reviews: i bought three hats to try out .... this one i like the best ..... the others have a upside down bowl appearance to them which really don't like (right up there with wearing them backwards :) Probably going to order at least one more in a different color. Shipping was great as usual (except when amazon uses intelcom)
product_name: JAMONT Unisex Cotton Adjustable Plain Hat Baseball Cap Multi Colors

reviews: Product arrived exactly how it looked in the pictures. This is probably one of my new favorite go-to caps for its quality and fit. It's got a stiff crown and is high-profile, so if you have a small head I can see these hats being a tad too big for you. I have a big head so this hat is perfect for me.
product_name: JAMONT Unisex Cotton Adjustable Plain Hat Baseball Cap Multi Colors

review_title: Hat fits pretty good, but will be sending it back
reviews:
Hat fits pretty good, but will be sending it back.
My "Light Grey" showed up as a "Faint Purple".
This wasn't my mistake by wrong colour choice....it just was an attempt at a greyish colour.
product_name: JAMONT Unisex Cotton Adjustable Plain Hat Baseball Cap Multi Colors

reviews:
Bought it for my son but I liked it so I kept it for myself !
Thank you, Amazon !
Lisa Benedix, Grand Lake NB
product_name: JAMONT Unisex Cotton Adjustable Plain Hat Baseball Cap Multi Colors

reviews: specified size does not match
product_name: JAMONT Unisex Cotton Adjustable Plain Hat Baseball Cap Multi Colors

reviews: Be aware if you like your ball cap to sit down on your head this one isn't for you. The lining in the front of the cap makes it stiff and it sits up too high and has 3 points. Not liking it. Material is good, color is good.
product_name: JAMONT Unisex Cotton Adjustable Plain Hat Baseball Cap Multi Colors

review_title: Slightly smaller than expected, not enought to prevent wearing.
reviews: Decent, not defects. I found that despite the capacity to be adjusted the circumference is a tad to small, so it feel a bit tight around my head.
product_name: JAMONT Unisex Cotton Adjustable Plain Hat Baseball Cap Multi Colors

reviews: Made for people with gigantic heads
product_name: JAMONT Unisex Cotton Adjustable Plain Hat Baseball Cap Multi Colors

reviews: Really is a nice hat, decent quality and no problems - well, almost. I'm only giving 3 stars because if I had known how tall (and structured) it is, I wouldn't have bought it. I'll keep it and use it as a back-up for the perfect hat that I'm still searching for - my last perfect one saved me from a bird bombardment, and even after a thorough cleaning, it just isn't the same (and I don't just mean the discolouration).

product_name: JAMONT Unisex Cotton Adjustable Plain Hat Baseball Cap Multi Colors

reviews: Made for people with gigantic heads
product_name: JAMONT Unisex Cotton Adjustable Plain Hat Baseball Cap Multi Colors

reviews: Really is a nice hat, decent quality and no problems - well, almost. I'm only giving 3 stars because if I had known how tall (and structured) it is, I wouldn't have bought it. I'll keep it and use it as a back-up for the perfect hat that I'm still searching for - my last perfect one saved me from a bird bombardment, and even after a thorough cleaning, it just isn't the same (and I don't just mean the discolouration).
product_name: JAMONT Unisex Cotton Adjustable Plain Hat Baseball Cap Multi Colors

review_title: Quality hat. Only issue is it catches lint easily.
reviews: Bought two hats from different sellers on Amazon. The other one was harder and thicker material which caused irritation were my ears rubbed on the edge. This one is much more comfortable. Seems durable, too. Only complaint is the finish of the material seems to catch a lot of lint and pet hair that is hard to remove.
product_name: JAMONT Unisex Cotton Adjustable Plain Hat Baseball Cap Multi Colors

review_title: this one i like the best
reviews: i bought three hats to try out .... this one i like the best ..... the others have a upside down bowl appearance to them which really don't like (right up there with wearing them backwards :) Probably going to order at least one more in a different color. Shipping was great as usual (except when amazon uses intelcom)
product_name: JAMONT Unisex Cotton Adjustable Plain Hat Baseball Cap Multi Colors

reviews: Product arrived exactly how it looked in the pictures. This is probably one of my new favorite go-to caps for its quality and fit. It's got a stiff crown and is high-profile, so if you have a small head I can see these hats being a tad too big for you. I have a big head so this hat is perfect for me.
product_name: JAMONT Unisex Cotton Adjustable Plain Hat Baseball Cap Multi Colors

reviews: Be aware if you like your ball cap to sit down on your head this one isn't for you. The lining in the front of the cap makes it stiff and it sits up too high and has 3 points. Not liking it. Material is good, color is good.
product_name: JAMONT Unisex Cotton Adjustable Plain Hat Baseball Cap Multi Colors

review_title: Slightly smaller than expected, not enought to prevent wearing.
reviews: Decent, not defects. I found that despite the capacity to be adjusted the circumference is a tad to small, so it feel a bit tight around my head.
product_name: JAMONT Unisex Cotton Adjustable Plain Hat Baseball Cap Multi Colors

reviews: Made for people with gigantic heads
product_name: JAMONT Unisex Cotton Adjustable Plain Hat Baseball Cap Multi Colors

reviews: Really is a nice hat, decent quality and no problems - well, almost. I'm only giving 3 stars because if I had known how tall (and structured) it is, I wouldn't have bought it. I'll keep it and use it as a back-up for the perfect hat that I'm still searching for - my last perfect one saved me from a bird bombardment, and even after a thorough cleaning, it just isn't the same (and I don't just mean the discolouration).
product_name: JAMONT Unisex Cotton Adjustable Plain Hat Baseball Cap Multi Colors

review_title: Quality hat. Only issue is it catches lint easily.
reviews: Bought two hats from different sellers on Amazon. The other one was harder and thicker material which caused irritation were my ears rubbed on the edge. This one is much more comfortable. Seems durable, too. Only complaint is the finish of the material seems to catch a lot of lint and pet hair that is hard to remove.
product_name: JAMONT Unisex Cotton Adjustable Plain Hat Baseball Cap Multi Colors

review_title: this one i like the best
reviews: i bought three hats to try out .... this one i like the best ..... the others have a upside down bowl appearance to them which really don't like (right up there with wearing them backwards :) Probably going to order at least one more in a different color. Shipping was great as usual (except when amazon uses intelcom)
product_name: JAMONT Unisex Cotton Adjustable Plain Hat Baseball Cap Multi Colors

reviews: Product arrived exactly how it looked in the pictures. This is probably one of my new favorite go-to caps for its quality and fit. It's got a stiff crown and is high-profile, so if you have a small head I can see these hats being a tad too big for you. I have a big head so this hat is perfect for me.

reviews: Bought two hats from different sellers on Amazon. The other one was harder and thicker material which caused irritation were my ears rubbed on the edge. This one is much more comfortable. Seems durable, too. Only complaint is the finish of the material seems to catch a lot of lint and pet hair that is hard to remove.
product_name: JAMONT Unisex Cotton Adjustable Plain Hat Baseball Cap Multi Colors

review_title: this one i like the best
reviews: i bought three hats to try out .... this one i like the best ..... the others have a upside down bowl appearance to them which really don't like (right up there with wearing them backwards :) Probably going to order at least one more in a different color. Shipping was great as usual (except when amazon uses intelcom)
product_name: JAMONT Unisex Cotton Adjustable Plain Hat Baseball Cap Multi Colors

reviews: Product arrived exactly how it looked in the pictures. This is probably one of my new favorite go-to caps for its quality and fit. It's got a stiff crown and is high-profile, so if you have a small head I can see these hats being a tad too big for you. I have a big head so this hat is perfect for me.
product_name: JAMONT Unisex Cotton Adjustable Plain Hat Baseball Cap Multi Colors

review_title: Hat fits pretty good, but will be sending it back
reviews:
Hat fits pretty good, but will be sending it back.
My "Light Grey" showed up as a "Faint Purple".
This wasn't my mistake by wrong colour choice....it just was an attempt at a greyish colour.
product_name: JAMONT Unisex Cotton Adjustable Plain Hat Baseball Cap Multi Colors

reviews:
Bought it for my son but I liked it so I kept it for myself !
Thank you, Amazon !
Lisa Benedix, Grand Lake NB
product_name: JAMONT Unisex Cotton Adjustable Plain Hat Baseball Cap Multi Colors

reviews: specified size does not match
product_name: JAMONT Unisex Cotton Adjustable Plain Hat Baseball Cap Multi Colors

reviews: Be aware if you like your ball cap to sit down on your head this one isn't for you. The lining in the front of the cap makes it stiff and it sits up too high and has 3 points. Not liking it. Material is good, color is good.
product_name: JAMONT Unisex Cotton Adjustable Plain Hat Baseball Cap Multi Colors

review_title: Slightly smaller than expected, not enought to prevent wearing.
reviews: Decent, not defects. I found that despite the capacity to be adjusted the circumference is a tad to small, so it feel a bit tight around my head.
product_name: JAMONT Unisex Cotton Adjustable Plain Hat Baseball Cap Multi Colors

reviews: Made for people with gigantic heads
product_name: JAMONT Unisex Cotton Adjustable Plain Hat Baseball Cap Multi Colors

reviews: Really is a nice hat, decent quality and no problems - well, almost. I'm only giving 3 stars because if I had known how tall (and structured) it is, I wouldn't have bought it. I'll keep it and use it as a back-up for the perfect hat that I'm still searching for - my last perfect one saved me from a bird bombardment, and even after a thorough cleaning, it just isn't the same (and I don't just mean the discolouration).

product_name: JAMONT Unisex Cotton Adjustable Plain Hat Baseball Cap Multi Colors

reviews: Made for people with gigantic heads
product_name: JAMONT Unisex Cotton Adjustable Plain Hat Baseball Cap Multi Colors

reviews: Really is a nice hat, decent quality and no problems - well, almost. I'm only giving 3 stars because if I had known how tall (and structured) it is, I wouldn't have bought it. I'll keep it and use it as a back-up for the perfect hat that I'm still searching for - my last perfect one saved me from a bird bombardment, and even after a thorough cleaning, it just isn't the same (and I don't just mean the discolouration).
product_name: JAMONT Unisex Cotton Adjustable Plain Hat Baseball Cap Multi Colors

review_title: Quality hat. Only issue is it catches lint easily.
reviews: Bought two hats from different sellers on Amazon. The other one was harder and thicker material which caused irritation were my ears rubbed on the edge. This one is much more comfortable. Seems durable, too. Only complaint is the finish of the material seems to catch a lot of lint and pet hair that is hard to remove.
product_name: JAMONT Unisex Cotton Adjustable Plain Hat Baseball Cap Multi Colors

review_title: this one i like the best
reviews: i bought three hats to try out .... this one i like the best ..... the others have a upside down bowl appearance to them which really don't like (right up there with wearing them backwards :) Probably going to order at least one more in a different color. Shipping was great as usual (except when amazon uses intelcom)
product_name: JAMONT Unisex Cotton Adjustable Plain Hat Baseball Cap Multi Colors

reviews: Product arrived exactly how it looked in the pictures. This is probably one of my new favorite go-to caps for its quality and fit. It's got a stiff crown and is high-profile, so if you have a small head I can see these hats being a tad too big for you. I have a big head so this hat is perfect for me.
product_name: JAMONT Unisex Cotton Adjustable Plain Hat Baseball Cap Multi Colors

review_title: Be very careful buying an Under Armour cap over the internet.
reviews: The cap was fine, the shipping was fast and Amazon stands behind their products so I can return it but anyone buying a Under Armour cap over the internet is taking a big chance that likely won't work out. Problem is Under Armour's sizes. . After measuring my head carefully I ordered the cap in large/xlarge. Cap was way too tight to wear for more than a few minutes. Amazon was happy to take it back. So I ordered the same cap but next size larger from somewhere else because they had the colour I wanted and Amazon didn't it. The second Under Armour cap was way too large. Either Under Armour's sizing needs to be revised or their quality control of sizes is lacking.

review_title: Buy one size larger (it stretches) - Great hat, good for hot weather
reviews:
While I'm not a fan of the small bill of the the hat, I do love the fact that it breathe REALLY well compared to conventional hats from LIDS. Any slight gust of wind you can feel in your hair and scalp and cools you down much more than any other hat will. The fabric is made of a stretchy mesh that is very breathable and allows you to cool down, whether its a hot day or you're playing sports. The hat fits smaller compared to LIDS hats. Despite that it can be worn comfortably for hours without any issues.

This hat is great. It looks nice, it allows me to stay cool, and it's cheaper than most hats you see in sports stores even though it's made of better material. If you're in the market for a hat, this is a good place to start.

review_title: Received a defective hat and then a 2nd defective hat - Poor stitching and off-centre bill/crown
reviews:
Got two of these, both had defects with how the bill and the front panels are stitched together. The centre of the bill and the centre of the hat were not aligned. In addition the stitching overall was full of noticeable errors in manufacturing giving it a weird fit.

I bought the large size and it fit well overall, but due to the errors it looked terrible. I got a replacement, similar issues. May just be a certain run that Amazon got, but 2 strikes and you're out! I returned both pairs.
